title: Alexis Thunderstorm 500 with Alaska Thunderf*ck
description:
Alaska 5000 talks beauty icons, making catchy music, and finally realizing how beautiful she is while on molly at Burning Man.
Brace yourself for some not-so-glamorous drag memories, nostril waxing, and what the hell is ear candling? 

To follow Alaska: @theonlyalaska5000
To follow Trixie: @TrixieMattel
To follow Katya: @Katya_Zamo
To listen to our podcast on YouTube: http://bit.ly/TBATBYT
